hopobject.body: I support Manchester United vinarol st Aguilera challenged two of her artists, Josh Logan and Michael Lynch, with a song by Levine’s band, Maroon 5: “Harder To Breathe.” Green correctly pointed out that Logan’s vocals sounded very similar to that of Levine. Levine noted that Logan’s voice is more masculine than his. Levine said that while both artists did an amazing job, he favored Logan. Aguilera declared Logan the winner, and Lynch was sent home.
